                     <interp inst="t17960406-29-punish172" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="publicWhipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-29-defend318 t17960406-29-punish172"></join>
               Publickly whipped
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. 
